    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, though upon close inspection, you will find some typical minor road wear such as a few small stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches near the door handles. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with the leather seats showing only minor creasing from regular use. All electronic features are fully functional, and the engine runs smoothly with a complete service history available. This is a reliable, attractive car that offers great value for a driver looking for a well-cared-for pre-owned vehicle.",
