    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Mechanically peerless and rigorously inspected, it represents the pinnacle of its class for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection. Available now for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
