      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This car has been babied since the moment I got it\u2014always garage-kept and detailed regularly. It honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you've been looking for that perfect, 'like-new' feel without the brand-new price tag, you've found it! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy this beauty as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
