      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Laguna Seca Blue. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 power plant, showcasing exceptional compression across all cylinders and a redline-reaching linear power band. Critical preventative maintenance is fully documented, including a comprehensive double-VANOS rebuild, rod bearing replacement with VAC treated shells, and a proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains true, benefiting from refreshed OEM bushings and Bilstein dampers. This is a true driver\u2019s car preserved in its most desirable mechanical state, free of leaks, ECU modifications, or structural fatigue.",
      "price": 48500.0,
